# Results and Analysis

## Dataset Summary

| Metric                           | Value   |
| -------------------------------- | ------- |
| Original Records                 | 9,082   |
| Original Features                | 3,925   |
| Final Features After Engineering | 4,696   |
| Normal Accounts                  | 9,001   |
| Mule Accounts                    | 81      |
| Class Imbalance Ratio            | 111 : 1 |

The dataset exhibited severe class imbalance, with suspicious mule accounts representing less than 1% of all records.

To address this issue, class weighting was applied using:

scale_pos_weight = 111.12

