# Threshold Optimization

Rather than using the default threshold of 0.50, thresholds from 0.01 to 0.99 were evaluated.

### Optimal Threshold

0.06

### Best F1 Score

0.9581

This threshold provided the best balance between fraud detection and false alert generation.

